OL,3,CBurnham thanks Glasgow for 'stepping
OL,4,Cup to save' Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FThe Games had originally been due to
OL,7,Ftake place in the state of Victoria,
OL,8,FAustralia, but concerns over rising
OL,9,Fcosts saw organisers pull out, with
OL,10,FGlasgow agreeing to host the event
OL,11,Fless than two years ago, in September
OL,12,F2024.
OL,14,FWith no public money used to put on
OL,15,Fthe tournament, a slimmed down event
OL,16,Fwill see athletes compete in 10 sports
OL,17,Facross four venues in the city.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
