OL,3,CBurnham thanks Glasgow for 'stepping
OL,4,Cup to save' Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FMr Burnham said: "In 2024, the great
OL,7,Fcity of Glasgow stepped up to save the
OL,8,FCommonwealth Games. My thanks go to
OL,9,Feveryone who made that possible."
OL,11,FHe added: "From my time as mayor of
OL,12,FGreater Manchester, I know the joy
OL,13,Flive sport can bring to a place.
OL,15,F"Glaswegians are good fun and will be
OL,16,Fthe warmest hosts to athletes and fans
OL,17,Fcoming from 74 Commonwealth countries.
OL,19,F"To the teams from all four home
OL,20,Fnations: good luck, and I'll be
OL,21,Fwatching."
OL,26,@nD@ROUqD@aO]sD@KOUwD@AOU{D@AOU}D@JO]
