OL,3,CBurnham thanks Glasgow for 'stepping
OL,4,Cup to save' Commonwealth Games
OL,6,F"It inspires people, builds stronger
OL,7,Fcommunities, and gives us all a bit
OL,8,Fmore hope for the future ` which is
OL,9,Fwhat I'm all about."
